{"tid":1717490,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沙田有住戶被TG射穿窗入屋","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:14:31.000Z","uid":308228,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"15537c14e513c79b27e1164d46e21f46ab721873","tid":1717490,"uid":308228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2391139911013207/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2391139911013207%2F&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4eyzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=8aa49bb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2391139911013207/</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田好運中心竹林閣5樓，催淚彈射穿窗户，直射入屋，並且爆開。<br />\n<br />\n2019年11月13日約21:40左右"},{"pid":"21a2593f876e9ee02dd0d4985cdc2298b21a1390","tid":1717490,"uid":268094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"終於"},{"pid":"bae66bd698b26ede646aebdc4d2e320e4da14524","tid":1717490,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"習曱曱"},{"pid":"2d776ae2bc5d7631f6cd744a6cdb1a71fa6b8f0a","tid":1717490,"uid":127469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"係咪有心射入屋？"},{"pid":"92ead46711b115aeaaaf3da0204edca361f5948a","tid":1717490,"uid":292789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"希望係藍"},{"pid":"7d54575b65ab1c3e25aa807bdfcc907c7461e3d3","tid":1717490,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"同實彈無咩分別"},{"pid":"1c98b72272a4cf0a3206bbb688565898a2cc9aff","tid":1717490,"uid":158332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母呀卜街黑警"},{"pid":"9dbac12e5badf550ce06dcfe8a6275c9aa9af2f8","tid":1717490,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JerhLyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJerhLyH.png&h=a8e9db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"2056d35cbd9a03b30c10bfb6c585e7c6fb6d76bf","tid":1717490,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"沙田有開花咩"},{"pid":"687a5615f31090189832e257cf537d1